@page "/"

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<h1>Welcome to TestResend!</h1>

<p class="lead">
    👋 Hello and welcome! This simple Blazor app lets you send emails using multiple providers—Resend, Twilio (SendGrid), Bravo, and Mailchimp.
</p>
<p>
    Explore the navigation menu to try out different email features like bulk sending, attachments, CC/BCC, templates, and more.
    <br />
    Whether you're testing, learning, or building, you'll find easy-to-use forms and instant feedback.
</p>
<p>
    Ready to get started? Select an email feature from the menu and see how each provider works!
</p>
<p class="text-muted">
    If you need help, check the README or reach out to the project maintainer.
</p>

